headline: Expanding Access in California: SmartVascular Dx™ Test Now Available Through Major Health Plans
summary: IRVINE, Calif., June 19, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- MorningStar Laboratories, LLC., (“MSL” or “the Company”), a leading developer of precision diagnostic tests that address unmet clinical needs, is excited to announce that the SmartVascular Dx™ test (formally known as the PULS™ Cardiac Test) is now accessible to patients throughout California.
